practitioner.about:
Dr. Laura Sloan is a General Dentist at Medcare Medical Centre. She completed a Bachelor’s degree in Dental Science (BDS) from the Dental Institute at King's College London. The Director of Education at King's College London awarded her the Gold commendation for professionalism. She also received an award in excellence for competency in Periodontology and Radiology.

Dr. Sloan commenced her career in the UK, by spending her foundation training year at Optima Dental Care, High Wycombe after which she did a long stint as a General Dentist with Bright Smile Dental Care at Kingston. She also worked at Victor Cockle Dental Practice, Eltham London and Oura Dental CARE, New Eltham London. Subsequently, she relocated to the UAE.

Her expertise covers all aspects of General and cosmetic dentistry. She is proficient in conducting routine procedures and examinations, root canal treatments, pain management and treatment of fractured or broken teeth. She also performs fillings, veneers, crowns and cleaning and whitening of teeth.

In her spare time, she likes to watch and play Football. She speaks English fluently.
